export const elementNames = new Map([

    "feConvolveMatrix",
    "feDiffuseLighting",
    "feDisplacementMap",

    "feDropShadow",
    "feFlood",

    "feFuncG",

    "feGaussianBlur",
    "feImage",
    "feMerge",
    "feMergeNode",
    "feMorphology",
    "feOffset",

    "preserveAspectRatio",

    "refX",
    "refY",
    "repeatCount",
    "repeatDur",
    "requiredExtensions",
    "requiredFeatures",
    "specularConstant",

    "spreadMethod",
